y love them in my house. Sure, the kids may need them roasted and showered in parmesan but they do love it! And that makes everything better.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-3.jpg\" alt=\"shaved asparagus salad with honey mustard vinaigrette\" width=\"803\" height=\"1100\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/asparagus-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Shaved Asparagus Salad with Brioche Croutons.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-3.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-3.jpg 803w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-3-728x997.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-3-768x1052.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-3-150x205.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 803px) 100vw, 803px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20803%201100\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-3.jpg 803w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-3-728x997.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-3-768x1052.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-3-150x205.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-3.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003