-150x199.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 830px) 100vw, 830px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20830%201100\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-4.jpg 830w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-4-728x965.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-4-768x1018.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-4-150x199.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-4.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe brioche croutons are so light and crisp. The pillowy bread gets so crunchy in the oven and it makes the perfect croutons. And while I love the big crunch, crushing the brioche croutons over the salad is my favorite thing to do.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIn fact, I do it with most croutons! It always gives more overall texture to a salad than regular crouton chunks. It’s just like having crunchy bread crumbs all over the salad.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-5.jpg\" alt=\"shaved asparagus salad with honey mustard vinaigrette\" width=\"883\" height=\"1100\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/asparagus-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Shaved Asparagus Salad with Brioche Croutons.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-5.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-5.jpg 883w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-5-728x907.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-5-768x957.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-5-150x187.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 883px) 100vw, 883px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20883%201100\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-5.jpg 883w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-5-728x907.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-5-768x957.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-5-150x187.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-5.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFinally, a big drizzle of honey mustard vinaigrette all over the salad finishes things off. Yes, I use this dressing all the time! It’s so tangy and savory with a hint of sweetness. Definitely a major love here. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-7.jpg\" alt=\"shaved asparagus salad with honey mustard vinaigrette\" width=\"804\" height=\"1100\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/asparagus-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Shaved Asparagus Salad with Brioche Croutons.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-7.jpg\" srcset=\