routons-8-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-8-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-8-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-8-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-8-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-8-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-8-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-8-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-8-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-8-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-8-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-8-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-8-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eAsparagus Salad with Brioche Croutons\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"98395\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eto 4\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e30\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e30\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eI love a good asparagus salad! This one is filled with shaved asparagus, chickpeas, sliced almonds and feta cheese. Topped with light and crunchy brioche croutons, the texture is amazing! Finish it off with honey mustard vinaigrette for the best flavor ever.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"98395\" data-servings=\"2\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecups\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ebrioche bread cubes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1 to 2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pure-olive-oil-25-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77600361?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eolive oil\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003epound\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003easparagus spears\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecan chickpeas,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003edrained and rinsed\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e¼\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/athenos-crumbled-traditional-feta-cheese-4oz/-/A-13308538?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ecrumbled feta cheese\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e¼\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/sliced-almonds-6oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77616858?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003esliced almonds\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"98395\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98395-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePreheat the oven to 400 degrees F. Place the brioche cubes on a baking sheet and drizzle with olive oil. Toss well. Season all over with salt and pepper.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98395-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eBake for 10 to 12 minutes, until golden and crunchy. While the croutons bake, make the salad.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98395-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eTo shave the asparagus spears, take a vegetable peeler and run it back and forth on the sides of the asparagus. I shave off as much as I can and leave the tops whole, adding it all to a large bowl. I find that moving the peeler back and forth as opposed to peeling just forward works great. Place the asparagus in a large bowl.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98395-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdd the chickpeas, feta and almonds. Toss everything with salt and pepper. Drizzle the dressing over the salad. Top with the brioche croutons, breaking some into smaller pieces. Serve!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003ehoney mustard vinaigrette\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98395-step-1-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn a bowl, whisk together the vinegar, honey, mustard, garlic, salt and pepper. Continue to whisk while streaming in the olive oil. This dressing stays great in the fridge in a sealed container for a week or so.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSalad\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-9.jpg\" alt=\"shaved asparagus salad with honey mustard vinaigrette\" width=\"829\" height=\"1100\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/asparagus-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Shaved Asparagus Salad with Brioche Croutons.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-9.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-9.jpg 829w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-9-728x966.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-9-768x1019.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-9-150x199.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 829px) 100vw, 829px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20829%201100\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-9.jpg 829w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-9-728x966.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-9-768x1019.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-9-150x199.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/asparagus-salad-with-brioche-croutons-9.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCrispy \u0026amp; crunchy!\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\u003c/article\u003e \n\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
